tle>   hehe</span><hr size=1> Yeah I knew braxom has another character Senjen. He sits right next to me in RL about 6 feet away. And btw he knew exactly what the guy was saying and said he could kiss off. And rightfully so, there was no attempt whatsoever to reson or ask for any sort of compromize. And if sombody in the guild would have asked me to leave because he complained to them. I would have told them to go sit on it also. Like I said I have 0 tolerance for rude people 0 as in none at all as in denatta period end of list. If your rude to me you get nothing and no guild leader no guild member no person on the face of norrath will ever move me in my stand. <br>
