<br>
This is assumeing of course that the conversation posted is correct. I assume it is since the second party hasnt claimed it wasnt (though they did add a previous part unknown to it).<br>
<br>
Both sides should understand that they acted in a way that offend the other. And if it is standard practice from them both, I forsee problems for both in the future.<br>
<br>
As the original camper, a tell should have been made that specifically asked the intention of the other, once it was clear both wanted the same thing. By the same token the second party should have been more willing to indicate a willness to come to some arrangement.<br>
<br>
