<br>
There is your willingness to negotiate. Your view on what is right on the server, and your form of sharing is clearly stated. That was said, btw, while you were sitting on the spawn spot. My, I'd have a great opportunity at finding him first, eh? <br>
<br>
You arrived at a camp that was obviously camped (the PHs were all dead). I have no doubt that you would share (even envoke PnP) if the jester had been camped by even or red cons to you. Since it was camped by players who conned blue to you, you simply ignored the fact that we were there. You could easily KS us. I did assume that you were logging out at first, since that's what respectable people do when they want to wait their turn for something. Ten minutes later you were still running around killing the mobs that previously had been a nice source of exp for me. It was obvious that you have no respect for your fellow players. <br>
<br>
This is not a PnP issue, btw. If you read the log, you'll not see any text where I claimed the camp as my very own, or demanded that the intruders leave. I only asked if he realized that we had been there in order to determine what kind of person he was. Sure, I hoped that maybe he was stupid enough to not realize we were there and then leave. I asked for an officer referral for the same reason, that is to determine if this was guild policy. You can read that intent in the log. I had already decided to abandon the camp. There are no items in the game that are worth real disputes. There are no items in the game that would compell me to banter back and forth with pricks like Dromel. I trusted his words in game. He stated his position and that is enough for me. <br>
<br>
For the life of me, I can't see where I was rude in this matter. If someone would be so kind as to point out the text, I would be grateful.  <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#d1c3b5><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title><A HREF="http://www.ezboard.com/promotions/csc.html" TARGET="_blank" ><IMG SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/image/cscicon.gif" WIDTH="20" HEIGHT="20" BORDER="0" align="absmiddle"></A> <A HREF=http://pub94.ezboard.com/utwotribes.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Twotribes</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC="http://ezboard.com/ezgfx/gicons/white_fire.gif" BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Board Troll</span><br>  Posts: 171<br> <font color=#A62A2A>(1/2/02 10:48:38 am)</font><br>     <br>Community Supporter<br> </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: Winds of Destiny?</span><hr size=1> I agree that the original poster was less rude. But your own words show no effort to offer a compromise. <br>
