Fact is neither side was right and neither side was wrong. Though the second group, in my opinion, had every intention of bullying the first if possible. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#d1c3b5><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub94.ezboard.com/bfirionavie.showLocalUserPublicProfile?login=dromel>Dromel</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br>  Posts: 17<br> <font color=#A62A2A>(1/2/02 10:57:19 am)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: Winds of Destiny?</span><hr size=1> &quot;You do realize that's what we are doing&quot; is a sarcastic rude and abrasive statement. Meant to raise a negative response from the person intended to hear it. Because for one I did not &quot;realize&quot; that you were camping him. And you knew I did not because you had NOT killed any of the place holders for him. You were camping the undead cook down the hall when we arrived. You moved from the cook camp down to the jester PH room after we passed you by. So if you want to get technical you didnt &quot;have&quot; the camp when we got there. You were camping an entirely different mob that has nothing to do with the jester. Consider youself lucky I even spoke to you. I wont make the same mistake twice belive me. <br>
<br>
End of discusion on my part rant and rave all you like. Ive said my part jerky boy can talk all he like. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#d1c3b5><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub94.ezboard.com/uglailfv.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Glail FV</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br>  Posts: 4<br> <font color=#A62A2A>(1/2/02 12:07:04 pm)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: Winds of Destiny?</span><hr size=1> I agree that you probably have said enough. Your guild may well deserve alternate representation. I'll spare the readers the word against word stuff regarding the physical events, but do want it known that our accounts are diferent. If a reader has a specific question, I'll be happy to respond. This is, after all, a public service announcement more than anything else. <br>
